{"tid":1497531,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"只要有錢 還有什麼不可以賣？","createTime":"2019-08-23T04:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T04:44:59.000Z","uid":4528,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5637a62f6835b32e27e9ff71a4e083bad1ffb916","tid":1497531,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:07:59.000Z","msg":"追求民主、自由 是更高層次的追求<br />\n係連登有人提過 出幾多錢可以讓你唔再出黎爭取民主自由 當時見到好多天價都係唔會出賣<br />\n但原來 一切可以係好廉價<br />\n只需要迫到你無左份工就可以<br />\n依家中共迫到國泰可以對員工政治審查<br />\n係網上發文都可以炒左你<br />\n有幾多人有能力可以承受依個後果<br />\n<br />\n如果有朝一日 我公司會因為請我而被中共針對<br />\n公司有會唔會有骨氣保住所謂爭取民主自由的員工<br />\n<br />\n如果中共散播的白色恐怖 慢慢散播到各行各業<br />\n我地又係咪有骨氣 或者能力去抗衡<br />\n<br />\n原來一切都可以好廉價<br />\n放棄的 拼命想走出去<br />\n仍抱希望的 它會摧毁你的想像<br />\n<br />\n只要有錢 還有什麼不可以賣？"},{"pid":"0038c0b716b85b40c81cb5c27dea71442cd3f28d","tid":1497531,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>所以我地更不能後退！<br />\n唔好失敗論！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU！而家搭車犯法呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9EGvnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9EGvnL.jpg&h=9da42bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKSEg2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKSEg2M.jpg&h=20a2e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/now5W2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnow5W2M.jpg&h=db034c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC19Ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC19Ef7.jpg&h=5ab15f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUdLW2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUdLW2O.jpg&h=132e85dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBjf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGBjf8.jpg&h=8a441805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgzvoHP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgzvoHP.png&h=79a62f84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55b89b44c13395c71a36063ef17e5dd46ccc7d09","tid":1497531,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:12:55.000Z","msg":"其實人類追求既野<br />\n係一層層疊加<br />\n首要既係對基本生活需求, eg 住，食，日常洗費<br />\n人類既instinct 就係「活著」<br />\n所以一定會優先滿足左以上需要先 <br />\n<br />\n我都個要爭取民主自由係好理想既諗法<br />\n但人類咪又係動物<br />\n動物有天性（eg 獅子食肉、牛食草）<br />\n呢d 係dna一早已經coding 左 <br />\nThat&rsquo;s why 白色恐怖咁有效<br />\n因為當中威脅緊人類對「活著」既instinct"},{"pid":"aec71d9170848af25871f7bda47cec80730f0eaa","tid":1497531,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:15:45.000Z","msg":"香港既真正國教就係錢<br />\n基督教佛教都唔撚入流<br />\n香港人基本上唔會同錢作對，亦都唔敢同錢作對<br />\n所以支共求其出下陰招已經令一大堆人跪低<br />\n<br />\n一個充斥左呢啲垃圾價值觀既社會，你可以expect啲乜？"},{"pid":"5dfe77b188c839d6657057f83ea4be90d09d4150","tid":1497531,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"UP乜鳩<br />\n冇左份工咪更加令我出黎反你中共囉<br />\n點解會覺得冇左份工就唔反"},{"pid":"6802350e68fdd99abeb41d74b99e5250fb1e8d95","tid":1497531,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:17:52.000Z","msg":"「千字文」毋忘初衷，我「反思」故我在<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497022</a>"},{"pid":"864e0e39c6b94a5a675ba4cb3e05985cad4f738a","tid":1497531,"uid":4528,"like":0